      "id": "2038952349176070270",
      "text": "The sub-agents section is the unlock most PMs are sleeping on.\n\nI run a multi-agent setup where one agent handles content, another monitors analytics, another manages my product pipeline. They coordinate autonomously.\n\nThe PM skill of the next 2 years isn't \"stakeholder management\" — it's orchestrating agents that ship while you sleep.\n\nBuilt a free eval to test where you stand: https://t.co/T0nTFzG2XH",
